JediTerm
============

The main purpose of the project is to provide a pure Java terminal widget ready to embed into IDE.
From this comes the name J(from `Java`)edi(reversed `IDE`)Term(obviously from `terminal`)

Licensed under LGPL.

Supports:

* ssh using JSch from jcraft.org
* vt102 emulation
* xterm colours
* back buffer so selection / cut and paste works
* scroll buffer
* terminal resizing from client or server side



Continued as a fork of a Gritty (http://code.google.com/p/gritty) by Robert Wittams and Omer Kudat,
which was in its own turn a rework of JCTerm(http://www.jcraft.com/jcterm) by Atsuhiko Yamanaka


